  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `PlaybookExecutionEngine.cs` around line 185 (`ExecuteChatSummarizeAsync`) to locate the existing prompt assembly + streaming call.</step>
    <step order="2">Read `AiAnalysisNodeExecutor.cs:442-499` to capture the canonical JPS `$ref` invocation pattern from Path 1.</step>
    <step order="3">Inspect `JpsRefResolver` constructor signature, dependencies, and `ResolveAsync` API.</step>
    <step order="4">Determine the DI registration of `JpsRefResolver` (likely registered already; verify in `AiModule.cs`). If `PlaybookExecutionEngine` does not currently depend on it, add constructor injection.</step>
    <step order="5">In `ExecuteChatSummarizeAsync`, BEFORE the LLM call, add:
      ```csharp
      var actionSystemPrompt = action.SystemPrompt;
      if (JpsRefResolver.HasRefs(actionSystemPrompt))
      {
          actionSystemPrompt = await _jpsRefResolver.ResolveAsync(
              actionSystemPrompt,
              scopeResolver: _scopeResolverService,
              cancellationToken);
      }
      // existing streaming continues unchanged:
      // StreamStructuredCompletionAsync(messages, schema, ...)
      ```
      Confirm `messages` (or whatever prompt accumulator) uses the resolved `actionSystemPrompt`.</step>
    <step order="6">Verify the streaming path is untouched — `StreamStructuredCompletionAsync` + `IncrementalJsonParser` + `FieldDelta` SSE emit logic is downstream and unchanged.</step>
    <step order="7">Add a unit test in `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/` that mocks `JpsRefResolver.ResolveAsync`, invokes `ExecuteChatSummarizeAsync` with a `$ref`-bearing systemPrompt, and asserts the resolver was called exactly once.</step>
    <step order="8">Add a unit test for the no-`$ref` path: when systemPrompt has no refs, resolver MUST NOT be invoked (avoid Dataverse round-trip on legacy paths).</step>
    <step order="9">Run `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` + `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/`. Must pass.</step>
    <step order="10">Measure BFF publish size; report delta vs prior baseline at `notes/handoffs/122-bff-publish-delta.md`.</step>
    <step order="11">Run code-review + adr-check (Step 9.5 FULL gates).</step>
    <step order="12">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 122 → ✅. Task 123 (streaming regression test) becomes ready.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="Read">PlaybookExecutionEngine.cs, AiAnalysisNodeExecutor.cs, JpsRefResolver.cs</tool>
    <tool name="Grep">Locate JpsRefResolver DI registration in AiModule.cs</tool>
    <tool name="Edit">Apply engine extension + DI fix + unit tests</tool>
    <tool name="Bash">dotnet build / test / publish</tool>
  </tools>

