  <notes>
    The streaming path is sacred per ADR-033. Resolution happens ONCE per turn at prompt-assembly time — adds ~100-300ms Dataverse lookup latency at turn start but ZERO impact on token-stream behavior. Test the no-`$ref` path explicitly to avoid regressions on legacy chat-Summarize playbooks (PB-001, PB-002).
  </notes>

